org.jboss.netty.buffer

Interface WrappedChannelBuffer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChannelBuffer, Comparable<ChannelBuffer>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DuplicatedChannelBuffer, ReadOnlyChannelBuffer, SlicedChannelBuffer, TruncatedChannelBuffer

    public interface WrappedChannelBuffer
extends ChannelBuffer
    The common interface for buffer wrappers and derived buffers. Most users won't need to use this interface. It is used internally in most cases.

    • Method Summary
